OL,5, The home secretary has told police     
OL,6, leaders to "ramp up" the use of        
OL,7, stop-and-search powers to prevent more 
OL,8, knife attacks and "save more lives".   
OL,10,FIn a message to all 43 forces in       
OL,11,FEngland and Wales, Suella Braverman    
OL,12,Fsaid the "dangerous culture" of        
OL,13,Fcarrying weapons must end.             
OL,15,FShe also called on forces to publish   
OL,16,Fbodycam footage quickly to stop police 
OL,17,Ffacing "trial by social media".        
OL,19,FOpponents of stop-and-search say it    
OL,20,Funfairly targets ethnic minorities.    
